colors <- c("OD 1" = "seagreen","OD 0.1" = "pink")

p1 <- ggplot(g, aes(x=Hours)) + 
  geom_line(aes(y = A1, color="OD 1"),linewidth=1) +
  geom_line(aes(y = C1, color="OD 1"),linewidth=1) +
  geom_line(aes(y = E1, color="OD 1"),linewidth=1) +
  geom_line(aes(y = G1, color="OD 1"),linewidth=1) +
  geom_line(aes(y = A3, color="OD 0.1"),linewidth=1) +
  geom_line(aes(y = C3, color="OD 0.1"),linewidth=1) +
  geom_line(aes(y = E3, color="OD 0.1"),linewidth=1) +
  geom_line(aes(y = G3, color="OD 0.1"),linewidth=1) +
   labs(title=" iLUX Lum",
        x ="Time (hours)", y = "Lum (AU)",
         color = "Legend") +
    scale_color_manual(values = colors)
p1

p1 <- ggplot(h, aes(x=Hours)) + 
  geom_line(aes(y = A1, color="OD 1"),linewidth=1) +
  geom_line(aes(y = C1, color="OD 1"),linewidth=1) +
  geom_line(aes(y = E1, color="OD 1"),linewidth=1) +
  geom_line(aes(y = G1, color="OD 1"),linewidth=1) +
  geom_line(aes(y = A3, color="OD 0.1"),linewidth=1) +
  geom_line(aes(y = C3, color="OD 0.1"),linewidth=1) +
  geom_line(aes(y = E3, color="OD 0.1"),linewidth=1) +
  geom_line(aes(y = G3, color="OD 0.1"),linewidth=1) +
  scale_y_log10()+
   labs(title="iLUX OD",
        x ="Time (hours)", y = "Log OD",
         color = "Legend") +
    scale_color_manual(values = colors)
  p1

r<- ggplot()+ 
  geom_point(data = data.frame(x = h$A1, y = g$A1), aes(x = x, y = y, color="OD 1"))+
  geom_point(data = data.frame(x = h$C1, y = g$C1), aes(x = x, y = y, color="OD 1"))+
  geom_point(data = data.frame(x = h$E1, y = g$E1), aes(x = x, y = y, color="OD 1"))+
  geom_point(data = data.frame(x = h$G1, y = g$G1), aes(x = x, y = y, color="OD 1"))+  
  geom_point(data = data.frame(x = h$A3, y = g$A3), aes(x = x, y = y, color="OD 0.1"))+
  geom_point(data = data.frame(x = h$C3, y = g$C3), aes(x = x, y = y, color="OD 0.1"))+
  geom_point(data = data.frame(x = h$E3, y = g$E3), aes(x = x, y = y, color="OD 0.1"))+
  geom_point(data = data.frame(x = h$G3, y = g$G3), aes(x = x, y = y, color="OD 0.1"))+
 labs(title="All OVL",
